 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukobex.showPublicProfile?language=EN>KobeX</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/11/01 3:41:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Fast Walk vs Jboots</span><hr size=1> I believe it was posted on the monk board that someone with run speed 3 eventually outpaced his other character he had on follow that was using jboots.<br>
